batchMintBaalShares(address[]).details: If ROM is a Shaman: Allows minting shares of Baal DAO to become member

params.to: the list of initiate addresses who have passed their rites to become member

changeHatsContract(address).details: Points to a new Hats Protocol implementation Only callable by the wearer of the default admin role's hat Emits a {RoleAdminChanged} event.

claimStake().details: Allows DAO members to claim their initiation stake

cryForHelp(string).details: Allows initiates to log permanent feedback data on-chain

params.feedback: "Developers do something!" Doesn't change contract state; simply passes call-data through an event

getDeadline(address).details: returns the user's deadline for onboarding

getRoleAdmin(bytes32).details: Returns the admin role that controls `role`. See {grantRole} and {revokeRole}. To change a role's admin, use {_setRoleAdmin}.

grantRole(bytes32,uint256).details: Grants `role` to `hat`. If `hat` had not been already granted `role`, emits a {RoleGranted} event. Requirements: - the caller must wear ``role``'s hat's admin hat. May emit a {RoleGranted} event.

hasRole(bytes32,address).details: Returns `true` if `account` has been granted `role`, based on the account wearing the correct hat.

initialize((address,address,address,addr.details: Deploys a new clone proxy instance for cohort staking

params.caller_: the deployer of the new cohort clone

initializeHatTree(address,address,addres.details: create & mint admin hats to deployer & admin addresses DAO can grant/revoke adminHats (after topHat is transferred below)

joinInitiation(address).details: Allows users to join the DAO initiation

params.user: the address which will be activated for the cohort Stakes required tokens and mints soul bound token

mintAdminHatProposal(address).details: send proposal to Baal to mint another admin protected by Hats protocol logic and Baal governance

revokeRole(bytes32,uint256).details: Revokes `role` from `hat`. If `hat` had been granted `role`, emits a {RoleRevoked} event. Requirements: - the caller must wear ``role``'s hat's admin hat.

sacrifice().details: Bleeds the life force of failed initiates into the treasury

setMaxDuration(uint256).details: Allows changing the maximum initiation duration

params.newMaxTime: the length in seconds until an initiate's stake is forfeit

setMinimumStake(uint256).details: Allows DAO members to change the staking requirement

params.newMinimumStake: the minimum quantity of tokens a user must stake to join the cohort

setShareThreshold(uint256).details: Allows changing the DAO member share threshold

params.newShareThreshold: the number of shares required to be considered a DAO member

params._to: initiate address who has passed their rite to become member

slaughter(address).details: Bleeds the life force of a single failed initiate into the treasury

transferAdminHat(address,address).details: send proposal to Baal to transfer adminHat to new EOA protected by Hats protocol logic and Baal governance
